    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]

        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate2]" (0723d8ff)

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[IsPaid], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[PaymentDate], [t].[TracingCode], [t].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Count], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[ProductColorId], [t0].[ProductColorPrice], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[ProductPrice], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[ColorCode], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductId0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate1], [t0].[Description], [t0].[ImageName], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete1], [t0].[LastUpdateDate1], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t0].[Salescount], [t0].[SellerId], [t0].[ShortDescription], [t0].[SiteProfit], [t0].[Title], [t0].[Visit], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[CreateDate2], [t0].[DiscountNumber], [t0].[ExpireDate], [t0].[IsDelete2], [t0].[LastUpdateDate2], [t0].[Percentage], [t0].[ProductId1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate2]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[IsPaid], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[PaymentDate], [t].[TracingCode], [t].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Count], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[ProductColorId], [t0].[ProductColorPrice], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[ProductPrice], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[ColorCode], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductId0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate1], [t0].[Description], [t0].[ImageName], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete1], [t0].[LastUpdateDate1], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t0].[Salescount], [t0].[SellerId], [t0].[ShortDescription], [t0].[SiteProfit], [t0].[Title], [t0].[Visit], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[CreateDate2], [t0].[DiscountNumber], [t0].[ExpireDate], [t0].[IsDelete2], [t0].[LastUpdateDate2], [t0].[Percentage], [t0].[ProductId1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate2]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate2]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[IsPaid], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[PaymentDate], [t].[TracingCode], [t].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Count], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[ProductColorId], [t0].[ProductColorPrice], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[ProductPrice], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[ColorCode], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductId0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate1], [t0].[Description], [t0].[ImageName], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete1], [t0].[LastUpdateDate1], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t0].[Salescount], [t0].[SellerId], [t0].[ShortDescription], [t0].[SiteProfit], [t0].[Title], [t0].[Visit], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[CreateDate2], [t0].[DiscountNumber], [t0].[ExpireDate], [t0].[IsDelete2], [t0].[LastUpdateDate2], [t0].[Percentage], [t0].[ProductId1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate2]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[IsPaid], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[PaymentDate], [t].[TracingCode], [t].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Count], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[ProductColorId], [t0].[ProductColorPrice], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[ProductPrice], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[ColorCode], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductId0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate1], [t0].[Description], [t0].[ImageName], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete1], [t0].[LastUpdateDate1], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t0].[Salescount], [t0].[SellerId], [t0].[ShortDescription], [t0].[SiteProfit], [t0].[Title], [t0].[Visit], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[CreateDate2], [t0].[DiscountNumber], [t0].[ExpireDate], [t0].[IsDelete2], [t0].[LastUpdateDate2], [t0].[Percentage], [t0].[ProductId1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[IsPaid], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[PaymentDate], [t].[TracingCode], [t].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Count], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[ProductColorId], [t0].[ProductColorPrice], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[ProductPrice], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[ColorCode], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductId0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate1], [t0].[Description], [t0].[ImageName], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete1], [t0].[LastUpdateDate1], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t0].[Salescount], [t0].[SellerId], [t0].[ShortDescription], [t0].[SiteProfit], [t0].[Title], [t0].[Visit], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[CreateDate2], [t0].[DiscountNumber], [t0].[ExpireDate], [t0].[IsDelete2], [t0].[LastUpdateDate2], [t0].[Percentage], [t0].[ProductId1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate2]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[IsPaid], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[PaymentDate], [t].[TracingCode], [t].[UserId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Count], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[OrderId], [t0].[ProductColorId], [t0].[ProductColorPrice], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[ProductPrice], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[ColorCode], [t0].[ColorName], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ProductId0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate1], [t0].[Description], [t0].[ImageName], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete1], [t0].[LastUpdateDate1], [t0].[Price0], [t0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t0].[Salescount], [t0].[SellerId], [t0].[ShortDescription], [t0].[SiteProfit], [t0].[Title], [t0].[Visit], [t0].[Id2], [t0].[CreateDate2], [t0].[DiscountNumber], [t0].[ExpireDate], [t0].[IsDelete2], [t0].[LastUpdateDate2], [t0].[Percentage], [t0].[ProductId1]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate2]" (0723d8ff)

    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]

    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]

    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[Id1], [t0].[CreateDate2]" (0723d8ff)

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageName], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t].[Salescount], [t].[SellerId], [t].[ShortDescription], [t].[SiteProfit], [t].[Title], [t].[Visit], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[ProductCategoryId], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[ParentId], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UrlName], [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreateDate], [p2].[DisplayPriority], [p2].[ImageName], [p2].[IsDelete], [p2].[LastUpdateDate], [p2].[ProductId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreateDate], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[LastUpdateDate], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageName], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[LastUpdateDate], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p].[Salescount], [p].[SellerId], [p].[ShortDescription], [p].[SiteProfit], [p].[Title], [p].[Visit]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Price] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[IsDelete], [p0].[LastUpdateDate], [p0].[ProductCategoryId], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id] AS [Id0], [p1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p1].[IsActive], [p1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p1].[ParentId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[UrlName]
    FROM [ProductSelectedCategories] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p1] ON [p0].[ProductCategoryId] = [p1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductGalleries] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p3].[Id], [p3].[CreateDate], [p3].[DiscountNumber], [p3].[ExpireDate], [p3].[IsDelete], [p3].[LastUpdateDate], [p3].[Percentage], [p3].[ProductId]
    FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p3]
    WHERE [p3].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p3].[DiscountNumber] > 0
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
ORDER BY [t].[Price] DESC, [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [p2].[Id], [t1].[CreateDate]" (0723d8ff)

    WHERE [p].[IsActive] = CAST(1 AS bit) AND [p].[ProductAcceptanceState] = 1 AND [p].[Price] >= @__filter_SelectedMinPrice_0 AND [p].[Price] <= @__filter_SelectedMaxPrice_1
    ORDER BY [p].[CreateDate] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[IsDelete], [p0].[LastUpdateDate], [p0].[ProductCategoryId], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id] AS [Id0], [p1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p1].[IsActive], [p1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p1].[ParentId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[UrlName]
    FROM [ProductSelectedCategories] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p1] ON [p0].[ProductCategoryId] = [p1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

    WHERE [p3].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p3].[DiscountNumber] > 0
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageName], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t].[Salescount], [t].[SellerId], [t].[ShortDescription], [t].[SiteProfit], [t].[Title], [t].[Visit], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[ProductCategoryId], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[ParentId], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UrlName], [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreateDate], [p2].[DisplayPriority], [p2].[ImageName], [p2].[IsDelete], [p2].[LastUpdateDate], [p2].[ProductId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreateDate], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[LastUpdateDate], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageName], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[LastUpdateDate], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p].[Salescount], [p].[SellerId], [p].[ShortDescription], [p].[SiteProfit], [p].[Title], [p].[Visit]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Price] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[IsDelete], [p0].[LastUpdateDate], [p0].[ProductCategoryId], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id] AS [Id0], [p1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p1].[IsActive], [p1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p1].[ParentId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[UrlName]
    FROM [ProductSelectedCategories] AS [p0]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p1] ON [p0].[ProductCategoryId] = [p1].[Id]
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductGalleries] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p3].[Id], [p3].[CreateDate], [p3].[DiscountNumber], [p3].[ExpireDate], [p3].[IsDelete], [p3].[LastUpdateDate], [p3].[Percentage], [p3].[ProductId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]
        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]

    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]

        WHERE [p1].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p1].[DiscountNumber] > 0
    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]

    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageName], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[LastUpdateDate], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p].[Salescount], [p].[SellerId], [p].[ShortDescription], [p].[SiteProfit], [p].[Title], [p].[Visit]

    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[IsDelete], [p0].[LastUpdateDate], [p0].[ProductCategoryId], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id] AS [Id0], [p1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p1].[IsActive], [p1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p1].[ParentId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[UrlName]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]

    FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p3]
    WHERE [p3].[ExpireDate] > GETDATE() AND [p3].[DiscountNumber] > 0
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[ProductId]
LEFT JOIN [ProductGalleries] AS [p2] ON [t].[Id] = [p2].[ProductId]

""SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CreateDate], [t].[Description], [t].[ImageName], [t].[IsActive], [t].[IsDelete], [t].[LastUpdateDate], [t].[Price], [t].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [t].[ProductAcceptanceState], [t].[Salescount], [t].[SellerId], [t].[ShortDescription], [t].[SiteProfit], [t].[Title], [t].[Visit], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CreateDate], [t0].[IsDelete], [t0].[LastUpdateDate], [t0].[ProductCategoryId], [t0].[ProductId], [t0].[Id0], [t0].[CreateDate0], [t0].[IsActive], [t0].[IsDelete0], [t0].[LastUpdateDate0], [t0].[ParentId], [t0].[Title], [t0].[UrlName], [p2].[Id], [p2].[CreateDate], [p2].[DisplayPriority], [p2].[ImageName], [p2].[IsDelete], [p2].[LastUpdateDate], [p2].[ProductId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CreateDate], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete], [t1].[LastUpdateDate], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(1) [p].[Id], [p].[CreateDate], [p].[Description], [p].[ImageName], [p].[IsActive], [p].[IsDelete], [p].[LastUpdateDate], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p].[Salescount], [p].[SellerId], [p].[ShortDescription], [p].[SiteProfit], [p].[Title], [p].[Visit]
    FROM [Products] AS [p]
    ORDER BY [p].[Price] DESC
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p0].[Id], [p0].[CreateDate], [p0].[IsDelete], [p0].[LastUpdateDate], [p0].[ProductCategoryId], [p0].[ProductId], [p1].[Id] AS [Id0], [p1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p1].[IsActive], [p1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p1].[ParentId], [p1].[Title], [p1].[UrlName]
    FROM [ProductSelectedCategories] AS [p0]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]

    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]

        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]

    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]

LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [o].[Id], [o].[CreateDate], [o].[Description], [o].[IsDelete], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[LastUpdateDate], [o].[PaymentDate], [o].[TracingCode], [o].[UserId]
    FROM [Orders] AS [o]
    WHERE [o].[UserId] = @__userId_0 AND [o].[IsPaid] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]
    FROM [OrderDetails] AS [o0]
    LEFT JOIN [ProductColor] AS [p] ON [o0].[ProductColorId] = [p].[Id]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [o0].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[Id], [p1].[CreateDate], [p1].[DiscountNumber], [p1].[ExpireDate], [p1].[IsDelete], [p1].[LastUpdateDate], [p1].[Percentage], [p1].[ProductId]
        FROM [ProductDiscounts] AS [p1]

    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [o0].[Id], [o0].[Count], [o0].[CreateDate], [o0].[IsDelete], [o0].[LastUpdateDate], [o0].[OrderId], [o0].[ProductColorId], [o0].[ProductColorPrice], [o0].[ProductId], [o0].[ProductPrice], [p].[Id] AS [Id0], [p].[ColorCode], [p].[ColorName], [p].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate0], [p].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete0], [p].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate0], [p].[Price], [p].[ProductId] AS [ProductId0], [p0].[Id] AS [Id1], [p0].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate1], [p0].[Description], [p0].[ImageName], [p0].[IsActive], [p0].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete1], [p0].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate1], [p0].[Price] AS [Price0], [p0].[ProductAcceptOrRejectDescription], [p0].[ProductAcceptanceState], [p0].[Salescount], [p0].[SellerId], [p0].[ShortDescription], [p0].[SiteProfit], [p0].[Title], [p0].[Visit], [t1].[Id] AS [Id2], [t1].[CreateDate] AS [CreateDate2], [t1].[DiscountNumber], [t1].[ExpireDate], [t1].[IsDelete] AS [IsDelete2], [t1].[LastUpdateDate] AS [LastUpdateDate2], [t1].[Percentage], [t1].[ProductId] AS [ProductId1]

    ) AS [t1] ON [p0].[Id] = [t1].[ProductId]
    WHERE [o0].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[OrderId]
